        <div class="sect-title-wrapper">
          <h2 class="sect-title">First Steps</h2>
          <div class="underline"></div>
        </div>

      
  
      <div class="text-wrapper">    
        
        

        
        
          <p>I have drawn machines, contraptions and gadgets for as long as I can remember. As a child, the Wacky Races and Catch the Pigeon cartoons left a lasting impression, not because of Dick Dastardly and Mutley, but because of the wacky cars and aeroplanes.</p>
        

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         


         

         

      </div>

