        <div class="sect-title-wrapper">
          <h2 class="sect-title">Early Accolades</h2>
          <div class="underline"></div>
        </div>

      
  
      <div class="text-wrapper">    
        
        
          <p>Aged 8, I entered a national art competition sponsoured by Kraft cheeses. I won my age category with an inventive drawing of a cheese factory, boasting a Rude Goldberg style production line (my prize was a visit to children's TV art icon, Tony Hart, at the BBC's Bristol studios).</p>
        

        
        

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         


         

         

